'''公雞標誌'''（{{lang-en|The Cock sign}}）是位於英國[[索頓倫敦自治市|索頓倫敦自治市]][[薩頓_(倫敦)|薩頓]]{{tsl|en|Sutton High Street|薩頓高街}}與卡爾夏登路（Carshalton Road）十字路口的一個標誌，設立於1907年，最初是作為公雞飯店和酒吧（The Cock hotel／pub）的招牌，之後被改建為路牌和燈柱。公雞標誌於2018年4月被列入英國二級[[登錄建築|登錄建築]]。

== 歷史 ==
[[File:The_Cock_Hotel,_1789.jpg|thumb]]

[[File:The_Cock_sign_on_Sutton_High_Street.jpg|thumb]]
公雞飯店之所以以[[公雞|公雞]]命名是因倫敦和薩頓均為歷史上的[[鬥雞|鬥雞]]中心，<ref name=Morgan>{{cite web| url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=BS1oVQ6zTw0C| title=A History and Description of Sutton, Surrey, with a Directory of the Inhabitants: And Map, Showing All the New Roads| last=Morgan| first=J.| date=1869| page=4| agency=大英圖書館| access-date=2020-06-08| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200608111255/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=BS1oVQ6zTw0C| archive-date=2020-06-08| dead-url=no| language=en}}</ref>飯店位於倫敦和[[布來頓|布來頓]]之間的一條主幹道旁，曾被作為[[郵局|郵局]]使用。<ref name=Morgan/>公雞飯店曾為拳擊手{{tsl|en|John Jackson (English boxer)|約翰·傑克遜}}所有，期曾獲頒英格蘭拳擊冠軍頭銜（Champion of England）。<ref name=HE/><ref name=SCG/><ref name=BBC>{{cite news| url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-46618992| title=Listed buildings: Bus shelter and cattle trough get listed status| publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]| date=2018-12-20| accessdate=2020-06-07| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200611113834/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-46618992| archive-date=2020-06-11| dead-url=no| language=en}}</ref>1898年，一部分的公雞飯店因道路拓寬而被拆除。<ref name=HE/>

公雞標誌由金屬建築公司{{tsl|en|Hart, Son, Peard and Co.|Hart, Son, Peard和Co.}}於1907年建造，<ref name=HE>{{cite web| url= https://historicengland.org.uk/listing/the-list/list-entry/1450261| title= The Cock sign on Sutton High Street| publisher= {{tsl|en|Historic England|英格蘭歷史建築和古蹟委員會|Historic England}}| accessdate= 2020-06-07| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200611113822/https://historicengland.org.uk/listing/the-list/list-entry/1450261| archive-date= 2020-06-11| dead-url= no| language= en}}</ref><ref name=i>{{cite news| url=https://inews.co.uk/news/environment/listed-buildings-new-uk-england-scotland-181896| title=From a thatched bus shelter to 'The Cock' - Historic England's most endearing newly listed buildings and structures| author=Josh Barrie| work=[[i_(報章)|i]]| date=2018-12-21| accessdate=2020-06-07| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200607162910/https://inews.co.uk/news/environment/listed-buildings-new-uk-england-scotland-181896| archive-date=2020-06-07| dead-url=no| language=en}}</ref>最初設立在公雞飯店和酒吧外的木架上，<ref name=HE/><ref name=SCG>{{cite news| url=https://www.yourlocalguardian.co.uk/news/18298851.famous-sutton-high-street-cockerel-sign-restored/| title=Famous Sutton High Street cockerel sign to be restored| author=Riley Krause| newspaper={{tsl|en|Croydon Guardian|克洛伊頓衛報|Sutton & Croydon Guardian}}| date=2020-03-11| accessdate=2020-06-07| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200607162909/https://www.yourlocalguardian.co.uk/news/18298851.famous-sutton-high-street-cockerel-sign-restored/| archive-date=2020-06-07| dead-url=no| language=en}}</ref><ref name=i/>1914年飯店被完全拆除後，該標誌被移往{{tsl|en|Sutton High Street|薩頓高街}}與卡爾夏登路（Carshalton Road）交會的十字路口。<ref name=SCG/><ref>{{cite news| url=https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2018/dec/20/bus-shelter-cattle-trough-join-english-heritage-list-historic-england| title=Bus shelter and cattle trough join English heritage list| author=Mark Brown| work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]| date=2018-12-20| accessdate=2020-06-07| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200607165726/https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2018/dec/20/bus-shelter-cattle-trough-join-english-heritage-list-historic-england| archive-date=2020-06-07| dead-url=no| language=en}}</ref>約在1915年時，公雞標誌被改成路牌，<ref name=Londonist>{{cite news| url=https://londonist.com/london/news/sutton-s-giant-cock-has-been-listed| title=Sutton's Giant Cock Sign Has Been Listed| work={{tsl|en|Gothamist|Londonist}}| date=2018-12-20| accessdate=2020-06-07| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200607162910/https://londonist.com/london/news/sutton-s-giant-cock-has-been-listed| archive-date=2020-06-07| dead-url=no| language=en}}</ref><ref name=SCG2>{{cite news| url=https://www.yourlocalguardian.co.uk/news/17311140.sutton-high-streets-the-cock-sign-gets-grade-ii-status/| title=Sutton High Street's The Cock sign gets Grade II status| author=Nick Kituno| work=Sutton & Croydon Guardian| date=2018-12-20| accessdate=2020-06-07| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200607162911/https://www.yourlocalguardian.co.uk/news/17311140.sutton-high-streets-the-cock-sign-gets-grade-ii-status/| archive-date=2020-06-07| dead-url=no| language=en}}</ref>標誌上的飯店名稱亦被移除。<ref name=SCG/>

搬遷後的公雞標誌位於一根{{convert|3|m|ft}}高的柱子上，<ref name=i/>由[[鋼|鋼]]和[[鍛鐵|鍛鐵]]製成，<ref name=HE/>而該標誌在移往十字路口前掛有一盞[[煤氣燈|煤氣燈]]和兩盞[[燈籠|燈籠]]，<ref name=HE/>後來煤氣燈被改為[[電燈|電燈]]，燈籠則在1915年標誌搬遷前被拆除。<ref name=HE/><ref name=Londonist/>公雞標誌上的{{tsl|en|fingerpost|指路牌}}分別指向{{tsl|en|Cheam|契姆}}、{{tsl|en|Worcester Park|伍斯特公園}}、[[卡爾夏登|卡爾夏登]]、[[克羅伊登|克羅伊登]]、{{tsl|en|Banstead|班斯特德}}、[[賴蓋特|賴蓋特]]、[[米查姆|米查姆]]和[[倫敦市|倫敦市]]。<ref name=HE/>20世紀末，道路規劃被更改，但公雞標誌仍被保留，而標誌所在的十字路口也被稱為公雞十字路口（The Cock crossroads），<ref name=BBC/>距離原公雞飯店和酒吧的位置僅有數公尺之差。<ref name=HE/>2018年4月18日，公雞標誌被列入英國二級[[登錄建築|登錄建築]]，成為該年度{{tsl|en|Historic England|英格蘭歷史建築和古蹟委員會}}在[[南倫敦|南倫敦]]地區列入的三個地點之一。<ref name=SCG2/>2020年，公雞標誌被暫時取下以進行修復工作。<ref name=SCG/>

